for my profound defects.

510
00:44:09,229 --> 00:44:11,230
- No!
- You know what I mean.

511
00:44:11,231 --> 00:44:12,565
- Yeah.
- And, uh,

512
00:44:12,566 --> 00:44:14,359
I've just been
